# BibleNest App-Specific Patterns

## App Overview
BibleNest is a Bible study and spiritual growth application with:
- Onboarding flow (language selection, plan selection)
- Main app with tabs (Home, Search, Likes, Settings)
- Bible content and study materials
- User preferences and progress tracking

